9. Batch Module (File Processing)
Explanation:
The Batch Module processes large trade files using Spring Batch.
Spring Batch is designed for large-scale data processing.
It processes files using three components.
Reader
Reads file line by line
Processor
Validates and transforms data
Writer
Stores data in the database
Batch Flow
File
↓
Reader
↓
Processor
↓
Writer
↓
Database
Structure
Copy code

batch-module
├── reader
├── processor
├── writer
└── config
Example classes
TradeFileReader
TradeFileProcessor
TradeFileWriter
